    <p>She made a long and detailed tour with no planned itinerary, stopping with no other motive than <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="her unhurried delight in the spirit of things"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(她沉浸在事物本身不慌不忙的喜悦中)</code></b>.</p>
